==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Connubiality
<hw>Con*nu`bi*al"i*ty</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality
of being connubial; something characteristics of the conjugal state; an
expression of connubial tenderness.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Some <qex>connubialities</qex> which had begun to pass between Mr.
and Mrs. B.</q> <rj><qau>Dickens.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Connumeration</ent>⟦br⟧
